data.description: Seller has spent almost $400K on remodel! New everything! 50-year roof, triple-pane windows, new electric, new plumbing, new insulation, new sheet rock, new flooring throughout, new kitchen cabinets and appliances, new fixtures in bathrooms, new exterior & interior doors, new gutters w/leaf screens, new interior trim/millwork, top-of-the-line material used. Great room concept, wood stove, large patio, 3.6 acres all level w/mass fruit trees and vegetable gardens.
